---
title: Roast Tomato and Bell Pepper Soup with creme fraiche and homemade breadsticks
description: Tomato soup and warm bread is a classic combination—with good reason! This velvety and veg-packed recipe is no exception. Toppings of torn basil and creme fraiche elevate the texture and taste of this dish even further.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220915_R10_W42_IE_IEXFVCLV0134-1_KB_Main_high-5a69808f.jpg
